CTRL + K + C ---> Comment Selection
CTRL + K + U ---> Uncomment Selection

CTRL + K + S ---> Engolf Selection with XYZ (section, if, else, for, while, etc...)

CTRL + SHIFT + B ---> Build Solution

CTRL + ALT + LMB(Click) ---> Edit Multiple Lines

Ctrl + R, Ctrl + R ---> Refactor (Change the text where the exact word matches by the given input) (CASE SENSITIVE) 

Ctrl + M + H ---> Collapse Selection

Ctrl + M + U ---> Uncollapse Selection

Ctrl + M + O -> Collapse All
Ctrl + M + L -> Uncollapse All
Ctrl + M + M -> Collapse/Uncollapse selection;
